{"tid":1927865,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"制裁港官如箭在弦  團體籲全民聯署 促美撐港雙普選","createTime":"2020-03-16T05:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T07:59:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"83e272881a73b0982c086970bbc342e3df44f5c3","tid":1927865,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:00:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200316/YSVAGAYOKT5KLUSHDCAGH23HE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200316%2FYSVAGAYOKT5KLUSHDCAGH23HE4%2F&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvo093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=675017d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200316%2FYSVAGAYOKT5KLUSHDCAGH23HE4%2F&h=5b4337a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200316/YSVAGAYOKT5KLUSHDCAGH23HE4/</a><br />\n<br />\n制裁港官如箭在弦 <br />\n團體籲全民聯署 促美撐港雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200316/large/1584288983_3ea9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200316%2Flarge%2F1584288983_3ea9.jpg&h=db28ee4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃之鋒昨發言指海外港人仍努力推動外國關注香港情況。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國國會去年11月通過《香港人權與民主法案》後，預計美國務卿蓬佩奧4月初完成首份年檢報告，民間集會團隊昨晚發起題為「美國戰線，如箭在弦」的網上集會，呼籲市民參與由民間團體發起的聯署公開信，促請蓬佩奧將香港民主普選進程列入評估準則，以及啟動對警察和賣港官員的制裁程序。<br />\n<br />\n記者：林俊謙<br />\n<br />\n「美國戰線，如箭在弦」網上集會昨晚7時開始，隨即為反送中運動抗爭中犧牲香港人默哀，香港大專學界國際事務代表團前發言人張崑陽宣讀集會報告時指，美國國務院日前發表《2019年度國別人權報告》，列明8.31黑警闖入港鐵的襲擊事件及新屋嶺濫捕問題，說明美政府對黑警違反基本人權、肆意凌虐示威者暴行一清二楚，即將出爐的年度認證報告意味美將重新檢視香港自治狀態，希望報告能將雙普選列為驗證香港自治最重條條件，並盡啟動相關制裁程序，懲罰侵害人權的港府官員和黑警。<br />\n<br />\n海外港人與華府商討制裁<br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊發言人劉頴匡指，何君堯等近日聲稱已獲100萬個港人簽名支持《基本法》23條立法，但民間團體發起聯署人數至今仍未夠十萬人，他呼籲香港人加把勁加入聯署（ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/LettertoSecretaryPompeo），惟有聯署人數才能證明港人希望美國政府實施制裁，又指國際戰線不能只靠眾志黃之鋒等人到國際游說，每個港人亦要出力，才能令香港國際戰線「有無窮無盡的子彈」。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FLettertoSecretaryPompeo%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%83%9F%E6%9C%89%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%AF%A6%E6%96%BD%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%EF%BC%8C%E5%8F%88%E6%8C%87%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%8F%AA%E9%9D%A0%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%88%B0%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%B8%B8%E8%AA%AA%EF%BC%8C%E6%AF%8F%E5%80%8B%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%A6%E8%A6%81%E5%87%BA%E5%8A%9B%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%BB%A4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A%E3%80%8C%E6%9C%89%E7%84%A1%E7%AA%AE%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E3%80%8D%E3%80%82&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvo093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=6c559d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/LettertoSecretaryPompeo），惟有聯署人數才能證明港人希望美國政府實施制裁，又指國際戰線不能只靠眾志黃之鋒等人到國際游說，每個港人亦要出力，才能令香港國際戰線「有無窮無盡的子彈」。</a><br />\n<br />\n英國領事館前職員鄭文傑、美國共和黨海外事務組織副主席俞懷松以及英國保守黨人權委員會委員Benedict Rogers等人，昨亦特別透過錄像和錄音聲援集會。俞懷松認為國務院日前發表的《2019年度國別人權報告》方向正確，「好消息是制裁將會發生」。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒指出，至今派出不同代表到世界各地做倡議工作，不少海外港人仍在推動當地政界不要忘記香港，身處美國東岸的香港民主委員會（HKDC）仍與美國行政和立法機關幕僚了解制裁細節如何才能成事。張崑陽總結發言時更表明，稍後會將香港人的聯署遞交至美國領事館，亦透過其他渠道直接接觸美國國務卿，希望國務卿能在向認證報告訴求中寫下更多對香港人民主人權發展有利的內容。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200316/large/1584288982_c8e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200316%2Flarge%2F1584288982_c8e3.jpg&h=fec6aad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英領館前職員鄭文傑拍片聲援集會。<br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n【AN OPEN LETTER TO U.S. SECRETARY OF STATE MIKE POMPEO | 致美國國務卿邁克．蓬佩奥的公開信】（Individuals to Co-sign 巿民聯署）<br />\n<br />\n聊署 link  : <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdYw2FJo-dZEEKMiSeXIF9Ih65NzvVKUbRdbnlk3-0K-wyGKQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdYw2FJo-dZEEKMiSeXIF9Ih65NzvVKUbRdbnlk3-0K-wyGKQ%2Fviewform&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvo093lW9tX0rIZwo7%2BvO8Vk%3D&h=5489a5c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdYw2FJo-dZEEKMiSeXIF9Ih65NzvVKUbRdbnlk3-0K-wyGKQ/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"ffb5871465386eb7f53f3f504beb039ed510e6dd","tid":1927865,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43c0b331130223b62277ae0511d8401357489ca","tid":1927865,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:35:43.000Z","msg":"所羅門及Benedict Rogers 都吹雞叫大家簽，有助美國制裁。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1927244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1927244</a>"},{"pid":"7749ded4fa454d19cd76d8199f033e16c78ea890","tid":1927865,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Share / forward / airdrop 乜都做！！"},{"pid":"0fb9de2f9c2eeb449d6788196b91fa17565d9145","tid":1927865,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:41:48.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b507f9fde474dbbd6fa02c55d326c24fcf0ad8","tid":1927865,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"推手"},{"pid":"8a2241930ce4b99e1da0b543c1f1c8e85ed780bd","tid":1927865,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:44:25.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c